T3-SA: Issue 98076: In Elasticsearch versions 8.8.2 to 8.9.0, using a global aggregation against a filtered alias with a terms filter causes all search requests to fail with an unsupported_operation_exception. A workaround is to replace the terms filter with a terms_set filter or a verbose bool / should filter without a minimum should match
